text: Kuzminskoye () is a rural locality (a village) in Meleuzovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 225 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 3 km from Meleuz, 1.5 km from Karan. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Kuzminskoye
